# TASK_PACKET

Task ID
CRUSHR-HARDEN-03F

Title
Pack pipeline separation and archive-construction boundary cleanup

Role
BUILDER

Objective
Separate the overloaded pack pipeline into clearer construction stages so that archive writing, metadata assembly, experimental profile handling, and low-level emission are no longer layered together in a fragile way.

This packet exists because the current pack path has accumulated too many responsibilities, making it difficult to reason about what is canonical writer behavior, what is experimental profile behavior, and what is low-level archive emission.

This is a pack-pipeline cleanup packet.
It is not a writer-feature expansion packet.

